Kara competed as a celebrity dancer in Let's Dance 2014 partnering with professional dancer Stefano Oradei.
She was eliminated on 4 April 2014 after her fifth appearance and performance on the show.
Kara participated in Melodifestivalen 2017 with the song "Gravity".
